Title: Designates a portion of the state highway system in the village of North Hills, town of North Hempstead, county of Nassau as the "Corporal Matthew A. Falcone Memorial Bridge"
Summary: Designates a portion of the state highway system in the village of North Hills, town of North Hempstead, county of Nassau as the "Corporal Matthew A. Falcone Memorial Bridge".
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a portion of the state highway system in the village of North Hills as the "Corporal Matthew A. Falcone Memorial Bridge"
